			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this step, the core team will begin to implement that community engagement plan.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="A community engagement plan helps you figure out how you're going to communicate and coordinate with community members. This planning process can help you expand your community network, enhance inclusion, and strengthen community buy-in and participation in next ERB activities.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Refer to your completed ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="Community Engagement Plan"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch2_CommunityEngagement_Plan.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=". Start with tackling the immediate action items you identified in the plan. Then, refer back to this plan as needed throughout the rest of the ERB activites.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Remember engagement takes time and the earlier you start, the better!">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
